headline: Atmus Filtration Technologies (ATMU) Is Up 5.3% After Boosting 2025 Outlook and Increasing Dividend
summary: Atmus Filtration Technologies Inc. recently announced that it raised its 2025 full-year earnings guidance following stronger-than-expected third-quarter results, with sales for the quarter reaching US$447.7 million and net income climbing to US$54.8 million. Operational separation from Cummins Inc., a 10% dividend increase, and a US$30 million share repurchase underlined Atmus's efforts to strengthen its market position and return value to shareholders.
